author: Brian Farmer
title: Gosha Rubchinskiy’s New Print Edition Is Dropping This Friday
text:
Visit the original post to see all 4 images from this gallery. 
Continuing his partnership with IDEA , Gosha Rubchinskiy is releasing a series of 100 signed and numbered white clothbound boxes that include five photographic prints and five graphic screen prints each measuring 16 x 12 inches.
Boxes will be released at Dover Street Market London and New York, as well as Comme des Garçons Trading Museum, Paris. Specifically, DSMNY will be selling the print editions beginning this Friday, March 24. If you really want a copy make sure you get there early!
A small number of signed editions (literally only five) have also been made available online , good luck!
